{"tid":515621,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔該開門]喺樓下屌鳩死廢老","createTime":"2017-12-31T15:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T20:17:41.000Z","uid":16951,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c3063db4bc9e034f6a1ddfdd4327edac23115e","tid":515621,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺樓下 前面有個廢老 大大聲係咁拍大廈道門<br />\n個保安阿嬸嚟 都無得唔開比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開完心佢 個阿伯仲要鬧個阿嬸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿伯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n阿伯：係都要人拍門先開既 慒下慒下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關之前我就係因為呢啲人 搞到我屋企道門比人扭開左個鎖 我一句屌埋去<br />\n我： 入憤墓咪唔洗撳密碼囉 就係你呢啲人搞到有人入左我屋企呀 死老坑<br />\n之後個阿伯眼定定望住我 屌又唔敢屌出聲 咁啱我有就走左無理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老實講 開比你係人情 你仲要喺道鬧返個實q 趁地冧啦死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb4c9259b07d9f085b0934077bceee58403a780","tid":515621,"uid":164928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"幫忙當應該 當自己係愛新覺羅"},{"pid":"8a0e08bc4b24f5e6425452a42449f33ef6e67554","tid":515621,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bb4c9259b07d9f085b0934077bceee58403a780","tid":515621,"uid":164928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"幫忙當應該 當自己係愛新覺羅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:21:17.000Z","msg":"真係覺得好黑人憎 仲要教返人點做咁樣 留返啖氣比自己過埋最後呢幾日嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d72e85f213def852b41bbb76454815bec69a2e","tid":515621,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T20:13:48.000Z","msg":"死廢老以為自己好特別一定要認得佢咁"},{"pid":"8295e421aff5ccd92dd2e3d8cea45b462070ed7d","tid":515621,"uid":8829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T20:16:24.000Z","msg":"看更見人就開門真係好危險<br />\n未死得仲有力氣出街又屌人既死廢老<br />\n自己撳密碼會死咩<br />\n一陣放左個賊入嚟 邊個負責"},{"pid":"37be17094f37b5901cb6bdb81136b85e200c034a","tid":515621,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T20:17:12.000Z","msg":"點解會屋企門比人扭開左個鎖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2db4da0a3eb1f6f4ddb1fde4d1f4fd00ea206e","tid":515621,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37be17094f37b5901cb6bdb81136b85e200c034a","tid":515621,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T20:17:12.000Z","msg":"點解會屋企門比人扭開左個鎖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T20:17:41.000Z","msg":"無野 未睇清楚"}]}